      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ICE COOL BLUE (4) turned in a better effort at Murray Bridge Straight last start, finishing second behind Neon Blue (17.25) in a TG1-4W. Has the pace to be prominent. Has never missed the frame from four starts from this draw, including two wins. Winning claims. ADHANA LAYLA (5) had been going along well winning a TG1-4W three back then placing at Mt Gambier before missing the frame latest when fifth (22.59) at Broken Hill. Can feature with the right run. OUR IVIE ROSE (1) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 400m behind Todd Keeping (23.22) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings seven times from 10 attempts. Should be about the money. WEBLEC SHIRALEE (8) cannot be left out despite racing here for the first time.",
